title: City launches Cultural Diversity and Inclusion Plan (Greater Bendigo City Council)
text: ( Source : Greater Bendigo City Council ) Monday October 19 , 2015 The City of Greater Bendigo today launched the development of the municipality's first-ever Cultural Diversity and Inclusion Plan at a breakfast forum featuring Australian Race
